        <span class="rev-stars-big">★★★★★</span>
        <span class="rev-agg-text">4.8 out of 5 &mdash; Over 10,000 verified reviews ↗</span>
      </a>
      <div class="rev-grid">
        <article class="rev-card">
          <div class="rev-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rev-text">"The charge pipe fit perfectly and solved my boost leak immediately. Quality is second to none."</p>
