          <div class="rev-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="rev-text">"Best fuel filter conversion on the market. Easy install and works flawlessly. Would buy again."</p>
          <div class="rev-author"><div class="rev-avatar">BM</div><div><div class="rev-name">Brandon M.</div><div class="rev-vehicle">2020 Ram 2500 6.7L Cummins</div></div></div>
