  <section class="slide" id="s4">
    <div class="s4-inner">
      <span class="s4-kicker" aria-hidden="true">🎆</span>
      <h2 class="s4-h2">Don't Miss<br>the <em>Boom.</em></h2>
      <p class="s4-sub">Sale ends July 7 &bull; Code JULY4SD &bull; 12% off</p>
      <div class="s4-actions">
        <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/sinister-diesel.html" class="btn btn-fire" target="_blank" rel="noopener">🇺🇸 Shop All July 4th Deals</a>
        <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com/shop-by-vehicle.html" class="btn btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shop by Vehicle</a>
      </div>
      <p class="s4-disclaimer">*12% discount on all Sinister Diesel branded products with code JULY4SD. Valid July 4&ndash;7, 2026. Cannot be combined with other offers. Excludes turbos, pumps, injectors. While supplies last. <a href="https://sinisterdiesel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sinisterdiesel.com</a></p>
    </div>
